Please contact Sharon (sharonk@austinsiameserescue.org) for more information about this pet.

//  I am a Black & White DSH, very silky! I am a great boy. Very lovable. I will make bisquits if you just look at me. I am also very curious and like to be in everything. Cabinet doors don't stop me (hehe). I get along with the other cats and like to run around and play with the toy mice. When I am done playing, I love to cuddle up in a nice warm lap. Rescued in Austin, TX and fostered there too!
